  "reset_password_title": "Reset Password - SolarOrca",
  "faq_search_placeholder": "Search questions...",
  "faq_q1": "1. I can't create an account. What should I do?",
  "faq_a1": "Check that you are using a valid student ID and entered the correct graduation year. If the problem persists, contact the alumni office.",
  "faq_q2": "2. I forgot my student ID. How can I get it?",
  "faq_a2": "Contact the alumni office at +86 123 4567 8901 (8am-12pm or 2pm-5pm weekdays) or email support@solarorca.edu.",
  "faq_q3": "3. I graduated but my graduation year isn't recognized.",
  "faq_a3": "Make sure you are entering the year you actually completed your degree, not the year you started. If you graduated before 1990, please contact support for manual verification.",
  "faq_q4": "4. I have multiple degrees. Which graduation year do I enter?",
  "faq_a4": "Enter the graduation year for your first/the earliest degree (e.g., your Bachelor's). Once logged in, you can add your other degrees (Master's, PhD, etc.) to your profile.",
  "faq_q5": "5. How do I verify my alumni status?",
  "faq_a5": "Enter your Student ID and Graduation Year on the signup form. The system checks these against alumni records. Once matched, your account is verified immediately.",
  "faq_q6": "6. My signup page looks weird. Help!",
  "faq_a6": "Please use a PC (desktop or laptop) to sign up. Our website has not yet been optimized for mobile devices.",
  "faq_q7": "7. What browsers are supported?",
  "faq_a7": "Our website works best with Chrome, Firefox, Edge, and Safari (latest versions). Internet Explorer is not supported.",
  "faq_q8": "8. How do I reset my password?",
  "faq_a8": "Click \"Forgot Password\" on the login page, enter your email address, and follow the instructions in the reset link sent to your email.",
  "faq_q9": "9. Can current students use this system?",
  "faq_a9": "Yes, current students can browse public threads and view class information, but they cannot post until they graduate.",
  "faq_q10": "10. How do I update my profile information?",
  "faq_a10": "Log in and go to \"My Profile\" → \"Edit Profile\". You can update your name, email, job information, academic history, and work history.",
  "faq_q11": "11. What happens if I forget to verify my email?",
  "faq_a11": "You will not be able to access alumni-only features until you complete email verification. The verification code expires in 10 minutes, but you can request a new one.",
  "faq_q12": "12. Is my personal information safe?",
  "faq_a12": "Yes, we take privacy seriously. You control who can see your profile, email, and phone number in the Privacy Settings.",
  "faq_q13": "13. How do I report inappropriate content?",
  "faq_a13": "Click the \"Report\" button under any thread or reply. Select a reason and submit. An admin will review your report.",
  "faq_q14": "14. Can I delete my account?",
  "faq_a14": "Yes, go to Settings → Danger Zone → Delete Account. This action is permanent and cannot be undone.",
  "faq_q15": "15. Who do I contact for technical support?",
  "faq_a15": "Email support@solarorca.edu or call +86 123 4567 8901 during business hours (8am-12pm, 2pm-5pm weekdays).",
  "faq_q16": "16. Why can't I see certain threads?",
  "faq_a16": "Some threads are marked \"Alumni Only\" and are only visible to verified alumni. If you are an alumnus, make sure your account is verified.",
  "custom_theme_title": "Custom Theme - SolarOrca"
}